OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Feasing during the early evening, then
OL,7,Fclouding over from the west with rain
OL,8,Farriving after dark and lasting the
OL,9,Frest of the night. Feeling rather cool
OL,10,Fin the strengthening southeasterly
OL,11,Fbreeze.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FCloudy and breezy, with rain
OL,14,Fclearing to the east during the
OL,15,Fmorning. Then followed by frequent
OL,16,Fheavy showers in the afternoon and
OL,17,Fwell into the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
