OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FWednesday breezy with showers.
OL,7,FBecoming more settled on Thursday with
OL,8,Fonly the odd isolated shower. Dry and
OL,9,Fsunny on Friday. Temperatures starting
OL,10,Fnear average, becoming very warm by
OL,11,FFriday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
